Redmine is a flexible project management web application.
Written using Ruby on Rails framework, it is cross-platform and
cross-database.

You may want to change $RAILS_ROOT variable (where redmine will be installed)
Default value: RAILS_ROOT=/var/www/htdocs

Create redmine user & group before running the SlackBuild script !
# groupadd -g 303 redmine
# useradd -u 303 -d /dev/null -s /bin/false -g redmine redmine

